00:00:12.478 --> 00:00:14.978
Bipedal, naked, large-brained.

00:00:17.645 --> 00:00:21.887
Long the master of fire,
tools, and language.

00:00:21.887 --> 00:00:26.041
But still trying to understand ourselves.

00:00:26.041 --> 00:00:29.343
Aware that death is inevitable.

00:00:29.343 --> 00:00:31.510
